<div class="container my-5">
  <h1>About Crypto Casino</h1>
  
  <div class="card my-4">
    <div class="card-header bg-dark text-white">
      <h2 class="mb-0">Our Data Sources</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="card-body">
      <p class="lead">This application uses data from multiple sources:</p>
      
      <div class="row mt-4">
        <div class="col-md-4">
          <div class="card mb-3">
            <div class="card-header bg-warning">
              <h5 class="mb-0">Coinranking API</h5>
            </div>
            <div class="card-body">
              <p>We fetch real-time cryptocurrency data including:</p>
              <ul>
                <li>Current prices and market caps</li>
                <li>24-hour trading volumes</li>
                <li>Price change percentages</li>
                <li>Basic cryptocurrency information</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="col-md-4">
          <div class="card mb-3">
            <div class="card-header bg-warning">
              <h5 class="mb-0">Categories CSV Dataset</h5>
            </div>
            <div class="card-body">
              <p>We maintain a dataset of cryptocurrency categories to provide context and classification.</p>
              <p>Each category has:</p>
              <ul>
                <li>Name</li>
                <li>Description</li>
                <li>Associated cryptocurrencies</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="col-md-4">
          <div class="card mb-3">
            <div class="card-header bg-warning">
              <h5 class="mb-0">User and Transaction Data</h5>
            </div>
            <div class="card-body">
              <p>For demonstration purposes, this application includes generated:</p>
              <ul>
                <li>Gambler profiles</li>
                <li>Casino tables</li>
                <li>Betting histories</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="card my-4">
    <div class="card-header bg-dark text-white">
      <h2 class="mb-0">Database Structure</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="card-body">
      <p>Our application uses the following database structure:</p>
      
      <div class="text-center my-4">
  <%= image_tag 'ERD.pdf', alt: 'Database ERD', class: 'img-fluid border' %>
  <p class="text-muted mt-2">Entity Relationship Diagram of the Crypto Casino Database</p>
</div>
      
      <h3>Key Relationships:</h3>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Gamblers have many Casino Tables</strong> - Each gambler can create multiple investment portfolios</li>
        <li><strong>Casino Tables have many Bets</strong> - Each table tracks multiple buy/sell bets</li>
        <li><strong>Cryptocurrencies belong to many Categories</strong> - Each cryptocurrency can be classified in multiple categories</li>
        <li><strong>Bets belong to a Casino Table and a Cryptocurrency</strong> - Each bet records a transaction involving a specific cryptocurrency at a specific table</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>